		<h3>Article 1 (Purpose)</h3>

		<p>Specified non-profit organization Niseko Area Mountain Bike Association. That is, in Japanese Katakana notation is written as “Niseko area mountain bike Kyokai” (Hereinafter referred to as "this corporation") comprises of Regular members, Adult members, Child members, Kid members, Family members, Sponsor members, Gold sponsor members, Silver sponsor members, Bronze sponsor members, `and Supporting group members. This agreement is established between the member and corporation in order to operate the corporation.</p>

